    <div class="inner-block">
      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>JP Marks was appointed Director General for Universal Credit Operations at the Department for Work and Pensions (<abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr>) on temporary promotion in March 2018.</p>

<p>Before this, JP was the <abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr> Universal Credit Operations Director and Area Director for South of England.</p>

<p>Previous roles in the Civil Service include:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Principal Private Secretary to the Secretary of State for Work and Pensions</li>
  <li>Head of Press Office, Corporate Relations and International Policy at the UK Pensions Regulator</li>
  <li>speechwriter to the Chief Secretary to the Treasury</li>
  <li>policy analyst at HM Treasury</li>
</ul>

</div>
      </section>

      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_4743">
            <h1 id="director-general-universal-credit-operations">Director General, Universal Credit Operations</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>The Director General, Universal Credit Operations is responsible for:</p>

<ul>
  <li>the day to day to running of Universal Credit operations across Great Britain via jobcentres and service centres</li>
  <li>the provision of all working age face-to-face services through jobcentres, including the relationship with employers and other external partners</li>
</ul>
</div>
            <div class="read-more">
                <p class="js-hide-other-departments organisations-name-list">
  <a class="organisation-link" href="/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions">Department for Work and Pensions</a>
</p>

            </div>
</section>      </div>




